"CHEMBL3588734"}, {"cofactor_name": "Garetosmab", "cofactor_resource_id": "DB16379", "mechanism_of_action": "Fibrodysplasia ossificans progressiva (FOP) is a rare autosomal dominant disorder of episodic, progressive heterotropic ossification.
